Package: recalls
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2014-05-09
Title: Access U.S. Federal Government Recall Data
Author: Thomas J. Leeper
Maintainer: Thomas J. Leeper <thosjleeper@gmail.com>
Imports: RCurl, RJSONIO
Description: recalls provides access to U.S. Federal Government recall data on drugs and food from the Food and Drug Administration, car safety from the National Highway Traffic Safety Administration, and product safety recalls from the Consumer Product Safety Commission.
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/rOpenGov/recalls
BugReports: https://github.com/rOpenGov/recalls/issues
